title: Cabbage soup
ingredients: ['1/2 medium head white cabbage, chopped', '4 large carrots, diced', '4 stalks celery, diced', '1 onion, minced', '175ml (6 fl oz) ketchup', '350ml (12 fl oz) tomato juice', '750ml (1¼ pints) vegetable stock', '450ml (¾ pint) chicken stock', '1 (400g) tin chopped tomatoes']
